These tests check that Flickr authorization works.
<dl>
    <dt>Open System Settings</dt>
        <dd>Open System Setting dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Open Online Accounts</dt>
        <dd>Online Accounts dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Add account...">Flickr</dt>
        <dd>Credentials dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Introduce the credentials (username and password)</dt>
        <dd>Permissions dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Accept permissions</dt>
        <dd>Keyring dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>When asked, introduce the password of your ubuntu user to access the keyring</dt>
        <dd>Flickr authorized account must be listed in Online Account's left column</dd>
    <dt>Open System Settings</dt>
        <dd>Open System Setting dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Open Online Accounts</dt>
        <dd>Online Accounts dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Click on authorized Flickr account (left column)</dt>
        <dd>Account is active (“ON”).  Gwibber must be listed as integrated application.  Dash must be listed as integrated application.  Shotwell must be listed as integrated application.</dd>
    <dt>Open System Settings</dt>
        <dd>Open System Setting dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Open Online Accounts</dt>
        <dd>Online Accounts dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Remove "Flickr" account</dt>
    <dt>Open Firefox</dt>
        <dd>Firefox will open properly</dd>
    <dt>Go to http://www.flickr.com/</dt>
        <dd>Credentials dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Introduce your credentials</dt>
        <dd>Online Accounts displays a new account for Flickr</dd>
    <dt>Open System Settings</dt>
        <dd>Open System Setting dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Open Online Accounts</dt>
        <dd>Online Accounts dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Remove "Flickr" account</dt>
    <dt>Open Chromium</dt>
        <dd>Chromium will open properly</dd>
    <dt>Go to http://www.flickr.com/</dt>
        <dd>Credentials dialog will appear</dd>
    <dt>Introduce your credentials</dt>
        <dd>Online Accounts displays a new account for Flickr</dd>
</dl>
<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'failed' result and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result.</strong>
